{"tid":1357654,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"所以文宣入黎！","createTime":"2019-07-23T18:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T04:30:15.000Z","uid":271687,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"746227452b08ef60fae5fb87e6e2ecba6f27a2fb","tid":1357654,"uid":271687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:25:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推</span><br />\n<br />\n請於下方公布所有香港之後嘅活動及詳情！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">讓市民清楚所有時代革命詳情</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🚨文宣🚨</span>"},{"pid":"b109b9ea86c5d3c7eea039370b1f5c045e46d29c","tid":1357654,"uid":271687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:26:18.000Z","msg":"文宣！pls"},{"pid":"9ca2bac740077802387476e32e438bec74ab87c7","tid":1357654,"uid":165246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:27:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"f7c1276a952bce3afe10ebf1f7d2e6b690212faf","tid":1357654,"uid":271687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:27:09.000Z","msg":"力推."},{"pid":"1467c8fb9f7ba93387353b1b4d4b0c18cfe60c78","tid":1357654,"uid":271687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:28:04.000Z","msg":"文宣！"},{"pid":"cf0558ac037ba5aa24acd6cf312a16cc6b840f02","tid":1357654,"uid":271687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e764f8f84c6c0dc4d1aaa68ab2169e5696df9b","tid":1357654,"uid":271687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459eff7caf18859374856ead3323588cfa6642bc","tid":1357654,"uid":258098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"746227452b08ef60fae5fb87e6e2ecba6f27a2fb","tid":1357654,"uid":271687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:25:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推</span><br />\n<br />\n請於下方公布所有香港之後嘅活動及詳情！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">讓市民清楚所有時代革命詳情</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🚨文宣🚨</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:30:10.000Z","msg":"🎆光復香港🎆時代革命🎆爭取五大訴求🎆<br />\n📢1. 全面撤回送中條例<br />\n📢2. 撤銷6.12暴動定性&nbsp;<br />\n📢3. 釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究&nbsp;<br />\n📢4. 全面實行雙普選&nbsp;<br />\n📢5. 成立獨立調查委員會，追究黑警濫用暴力，徹查警黑勾結7.21元朗恐襲<br />\n<br />\n[721]有手足頭部中槍危殆 吐血不止<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355224</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大穫到咁無外國人知? 我要將７２１上環最恐怖１分鐘半片段流出到國際 !!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n蘋果A2: 7.21遊行後爆衝突　 千警上環亂彈清場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1350647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1350647</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［整合] 7.21上環開槍清場 有片有圖！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348209</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n1. 有義士腳部中槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863977222448?s=1279554103&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10157863977222448%3Fs%3D1279554103%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdUy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=72c617ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863977222448?s=1279554103&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 有記者直接被催淚彈打中<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cTeVHAuMLP4&nbsp;&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcTeVHAuMLP4%C2%A0%C2%A0&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdUy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=7edd5bb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cTeVHAuMLP4&nbsp;&nbsp;</a><br />\n<br />\n西上環事件整合 求更多新聞同義士消息 推上去 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357053</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家幫手<br />\n1. 了解並更新上述受傷人士最新狀況<br />\n2. 找出更多未知義士受傷的資訊及片段<br />\n3. 廣傳讓更多人關注上環事發經過及受傷<br />\n<br />\n☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻<br />\n🥳7.24 港鐵不合作運動 時間:上午七時半<br />\n<br />\n🥳7.25 休息一天 (有待更新)<br />\n<br />\n🥳7.26 機場集會 時間: 下午一時至下午十一時五十九分*不反對通知書申請中*<br />\n<br />\n🥳7.27 光復元朗 時間: 下午四時<br />\n😎建議遊行提早於😎上午十時至中午十二時期間開始😎以確保安全😎<br />\n<br />\n🥳7.28 追究上環開槍責任<br />\n堅持五大訴求 拒絕警黑勾結<br />\n集合時間：下午三點（三點半起步）<br />\n集合地點：遮打花園<br />\n遊行終點：中山紀念公園（最接近開槍地點的大型公眾空間）<br />\n服飾：黑衫、頭盔、口罩（以示對警方濫暴不滿）<br />\n形式：和平理性．優雅自衛<br />\n遊行結束後請一同護送新界西戰友歸家<br />\n*將於星期三通知所謂警方<br />\n<br />\n🥳8.04 將軍澳反送中大遊行channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tko84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftko84&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdUy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=9742f7d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tko84</a><br />\n請各位努力推po以提出遊行時間修訂<br />\n已取消或延期:<br />\n<br />\n兩條戰線同樣重要 但係請各位心水清&nbsp;<br />\n任何一方都不能忽視 以防誤中港共圈套<br />\n亦避免被各方妖孽分散注意力 必須將火力對準政權<br />\n政府務必回應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n簽咗都要🙏廣傳🙏快夠數💪唔好話冇用就唔做，唔理效果有咩都必撐，團結是力量💪<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 21, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdUy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=aa6e40da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens</a><br />\n🖕🖕🖕見指中聯辦😡😡勾結香港黑社會😡😡策劃元朗恐怖襲擊聯署🖕🖕🖕<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/restore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frestore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdUy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=c07f3843\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/restore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0</a><br />\n🧐🧐【元朗黑夜連登獨立調查委員會】🧐🧐<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/34AmN69rRScNafEC9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F34AmN69rRScNafEC9&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdUy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=0575cdaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/34AmN69rRScNafEC9</a><br />\n😡😡投訴李漢民有違法公職人員行為失當😡😡<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\nEmail : csbcomp@csb.gov.hk<br />\n🙏🙏所有香港大學學生、舊生以及職員參與聯署，要求香港大學校長張翔履行社會使命。🙏🙏<a href=\"https://forms.gle/UAVikwsyCmdDEyy76\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FUAVikwsyCmdDEyy76&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdUy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=e1ead1c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/UAVikwsyCmdDEyy76</a><br />\n🤭我唔捨得何君堯去美國🤭<br />\n🥳大家快聯署留底佢全家🥳<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 21, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/make-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-visas?fbclid=IwAR0fZRhrobDg_hxUKcYKAN0XV833ZjHwxWu4XY82PzypubZpwq4ToZ8-e7M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fmake-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-visas%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0fZRhrobDg_hxUKcYKAN0XV833ZjHwxWu4XY82PzypubZpwq4ToZ8-e7M&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdUy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=25cd31e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/make-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-visas?fbclid=IwAR0fZRhrobDg_hxUKcYKAN0XV833ZjHwxWu4XY82PzypubZpwq4ToZ8-e7M</a><br />\n🥰🤩[遍地攬炒] 一人一信幫何君堯律師世世代代享受大灣區榮耀🥰🤩😁內含教學😁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351572</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡<br />\n銀行商店拉閘「靜過十號波」<br />\n指揮官拍膊與黑幫論形勢<br />\n大狀：必須獨立調查<br />\n警遲到場：睇唔到錶<br />\n999無人聽 市民向消防求救<br />\n「飛天南」蘇醒 稱被打無傷痕<br />\n林鄭重國徽輕視港人安危<br />\n記者叫特首「講返句人話」<br />\n王志民自誇中聯辦巍然不動<br />\n建制派反指示威者「挑機」<br />\n總商會轉軚促撤法：失職官員須問責<br />\n何君堯飯局 惡煞食飽打人<br />\n百人毀議辦 轟何勾結黑幫<br />\n被指撬閘 元朗區會副主席辯稱勸交<br />\n賴上環清場 盧偉聰：調配人手需時<br />\n元朗黑夜 還原白色恐襲8小時<br />\n休班紀律部隊自發趕到救人<br />\n搵仔媽媽︰警無資格𢭃人工<br />\n少年痛哭元朗沉淪<br />\n眾志成員遇襲傷頭<br />\n林卓廷轟建制無恥<br />\n青年護花慘遭狂鞭<br />\n柳俊江義載變血人<br />\n居民攜衫救人被毆<br />\n三區讓路 7.27「光復元朗」<br />\n巿民港鐵內受傷可索償<br />\n遇襲記者︰好似屍殺列車<br />\n不滿警黑合作 民政局職員疑罷工<br />\n國際將香港新疆相提並論<br />\n台灣不再信一國兩制謊言<br />\n警再開槍射頭 示威者重創<br />\n記者遭速龍舉槍棍指嚇<br />\n濃煙下槍聲四起 示威者變活靶<br />\n警不作為 黑幫肆虐元、屯、荃 變死城"},{"pid":"124650a244d2f9230876cee05f609558d6d44ff6","tid":1357654,"uid":271687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:31:21.000Z","msg":"所有之後落黎嘅革命活動,遊行等等都公佈下"},{"pid":"026e59c979c9cc4a0dd42bba4ed175dd61f20d7f","tid":1357654,"uid":258098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:31:39.000Z","msg":"我成日想搵宣言貼都搵唔到 唔該有見到推番上嚟<br />\n<br />\n宣言好重要"},{"pid":"1fdd09a5244b8d02ece48fe76833340a6abcc07d","tid":1357654,"uid":271687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:32:23.000Z","msg":"推上黎！集齊所有"},{"pid":"9761ab298403326502c4bd2992ea773227289d42","tid":1357654,"uid":264846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:34:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e394df360376246cbc8f223af97c06b974a26b9","tid":1357654,"uid":271687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:35:26.000Z","msg":"力推"},{"pid":"42db94f27a9b3ef1a7f1a5c8fe19560bcfa68cca","tid":1357654,"uid":271687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:35:46.000Z","msg":"文宣！upupup"},{"pid":"fcbe1231acd4f96b2677f26bed24cd28ece5316f","tid":1357654,"uid":286781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:39:44.000Z","msg":"【投拆Hi】一人一信俾條不生路何妖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357606</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ad93fbf7b0d6b8cd0e7c14c7d8b775300d0c3fc5","tid":1357654,"uid":237077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5aNwFaC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5aNwFaC.jpg&h=d84b994a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ede33870181ff6988acfb1f8287a481e262d65a2","tid":1357654,"uid":237077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9zOzCZH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9zOzCZH.jpg&h=e666996b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}